<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" media="screen" href="/~d/styles/rss2full.xsl"?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/css" media="screen" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~d/styles/itemcontent.css"?><rss xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:wfw="http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:sy="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/" xmlns:slash="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/" version="2.0"><channel><title>UNWIRE.HK</title><link>https://unwire.hk</link><description /><lastBuildDate>Mon, 28 Mar 2022 03:39:32 +0000</lastBuildDate><language>zh-TW</language><sy:updatePeriod>hourly	</sy:updatePeriod><sy:updateFrequency>1	</sy:updateFrequency><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/unwirelife" /><feedburner:info xmlns:feedburner="http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0" uri="unwirelife" /><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="hub" href="http://pubsubhubbub.appspot.com/" /><item><title>【教學】一鍵 LINE 備份與還原，一 App 完成 LINE 相片備份、LINE 聊天備份</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/03/28/linebackup2022icarefone-transfer/software/ipad-app/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=linebackup2022icarefone-transfer</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[AIpower]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Mon, 28 Mar 2022 04:20:03 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[Android App]]></category><category><![CDATA[iOS App]]></category><category><![CDATA[iPad App]]></category><category><![CDATA[社交網絡]]></category><category><![CDATA[iCareFone Transfer]]></category><category><![CDATA[line]]></category><category><![CDATA[LINE 備份]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1092280</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Apple 經常推出新智能電話、新平板電腦。買到新裝置，當然最重視社交通訊軟件如何從舊機過渡到新機。備份 LI [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p class="p1">Apple 經常推出新智能電話、新平板電腦。買到新裝置，當然最重視社交通訊軟件如何從舊機過渡到新機。備份 LINE 成為用家最關心的問題之一。而用過 iPad 版 LINE 的朋友也會發現，iPad 版並不支援 LINE 聊天記錄備份功能。其實你可以先將 iPhone LINE 備份，然後把 LINE 還原備份到新裝置，包括 iPhone 或者 iPad 上。到底如何備份 LINE 才是最安全、最快捷方便呢？小編以下介紹的方法，就能助你一鍵完成 LINE 備份、LINE 聊天備份與還原。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/13686795_1173430646053078_2233456530287017134_n.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1092288" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/13686795_1173430646053078_2233456530287017134_n.jpg" alt="" width="643" height="313" /></a></p><p class="p1">想 LINE 備份資料快捷，安全，手機用家可選擇「<a href="https://www.tenorshare.tw/products/line-transfer.html">iCareFone Transfer</a>」軟件（<a href="https://www.tenorshare.tw/">官方網站</a>）。iCareFone Transfer 可以做到快捷、安全、穩妥為 iPhone iPad 備份 LINE 資料、還原 LINE 資料，包括相片、影片、聊天記錄、音訊等等。用家只要把裝置連接到手機，即可把 iPhone iPad 的 LINE 備份到電腦，又或者另一部裝置。用了這個軟件，你可獨立為 LINE 備份，毋須備份整部手機裝置的資料，並能解決 iPad 沒有聊天記錄備份功能的問題，也支援 LINE 跨系統轉移，將 LINE Android to iOS。</p><p class="p1">iCareFone Transfer 軟件下載／詳情：<a href="https://www.tenorshare.tw/products/line-transfer.html">https://www.tenorshare.tw/products/line-transfer.html</a></p><p class="p1">官方網站：<a href="https://www.tenorshare.tw/">https://www.tenorshare.tw/</a></p><p class="p1"><b>文章連結：<a href="https://www.tenorshare.tw/line-tips/4-ways-for-line-chat-backup.html">LINE 備份聊天紀錄省心懶人包，2022 最全方案</a></b></p><p class="p1"><b>文章連結：<a href="https://www.tenorshare.tw/line-tips/backup-line-photos.html">LINE 照片，備份 2022 最完整指南，有效完成 LINE 相簿備份</a></b></p><h2 class="p1">備份 LINE、轉移 iPhone iPad LINE 聊天記錄步驟</h2><h2 class="p1">Step 1)</h2><p class="p1">首先下載並安裝好 iCareFone Transfer（<a href="https://www.tenorshare.tw/products/line-transfer.html"><b>產</b>品連結</a>），在主介面上，點選 LINE 為你的社交 App。（另此軟件也支援 WhatsApp、Kik、Viber、WeChat 的資料備份、還原與轉移，本文就以 LINE 備份作為示範）。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-24-下午 2.28.22.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1092281" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-24-下午 2.28.22-694x452.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="452" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-24-下午 2.28.22-694x452.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-24-下午 2.28.22-1280x834.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-24-下午 2.28.22-768x501.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-24-下午 2.28.22-1536x1001.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-24-下午 2.28.22-2048x1335.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-24-下午 2.28.22.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2 class="p1">Step 2)</h2><p class="p1">用 USB 連線，把你的 iPhone 或者 iPad 連接到電腦。當成功連接裝置，會出現圖中畫面，你可在拉下選單選取想備份的裝置，按「立即備份」按鈕便可。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-24-下午 2.31.51.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1092283" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-24-下午 2.31.51-694x454.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="454" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-24-下午 2.31.51-694x454.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-24-下午 2.31.51-1280x837.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-24-下午 2.31.51-768x502.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-24-下午 2.31.51-1536x1004.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-24-下午 2.31.51-2048x1339.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-24-下午 2.31.51.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2 class="p1">Step 3)</h2><p class="p1">接下來你只要靜待備份過程完成，畫面會顯示進度，過程中不要切斷裝置的連線。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-24-下午 3.04.57.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1092286" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-24-下午 3.04.57-694x453.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="453" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-24-下午 3.04.57-694x453.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-24-下午 3.04.57-1280x835.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-24-下午 3.04.57-768x501.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-24-下午 3.04.57-1536x1002.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-24-下午 3.04.57-2048x1335.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-24-下午 3.04.57.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p class="p1">如果你需要還原備份的話，就可在畫面左手邊按「查看&amp;還原」，你可把已經備份好的資料，還原到你的 iPhone, iPad 等裝置。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-24-下午 6.15.50.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1092662" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-24-下午 6.15.50-694x452.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="452" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-24-下午 6.15.50-694x452.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-24-下午 6.15.50-1280x834.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-24-下午 6.15.50-768x500.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-24-下午 6.15.50-1536x1001.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-24-下午 6.15.50-2048x1334.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-24-下午 6.15.50.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-24-下午 6.15.13.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1092661" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-24-下午 6.15.13-694x451.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="451" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-24-下午 6.15.13-694x451.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-24-下午 6.15.13-1280x831.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-24-下午 6.15.13-768x499.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-24-下午 6.15.13-1536x997.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-24-下午 6.15.13-2048x1330.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-24-下午 6.15.13.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p class="p1">如果你想從 Android 設備傳輸 LINE 數據到 iOS 設備的話，你需要把兩臺裝置同時接上電腦。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-24-下午 2.31.40.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1092282" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-24-下午 2.31.40-694x453.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="453" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-24-下午 2.31.40-694x453.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-24-下午 2.31.40-1280x835.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-24-下午 2.31.40-768x501.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-24-下午 2.31.40-1536x1003.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-24-下午 2.31.40-2048x1337.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-24-下午 2.31.40.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-24-下午 2.31.40.jpg"><iframe loading="lazy" title="YouTube video player" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/1qmAm0F0fpM" width="560" height="315" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></a></p><h2 class="p1">軟件價格、unwire 讀者專用優惠碼</h2><p class="p1">iCareFone Transfer 雖為付費軟件，但能為用戶帶來方便、安全的 LINE 備份方式，用家可考慮自己的需要而購買。一個月授權版價格為 HK$219、一年授權版價格為 HK$499，而永久授權版的價格為 HK$599。unwire 讀者現在可使用優惠碼購買，可獲 7 折優惠。</p><h2 class="p1">7 折優惠碼: A3KER6</h2><p class="p1">iCareFone Transfer 連結：<a href="https://www.tenorshare.tw/products/line-transfer.html">按此</a></p><h2 class="p1">總結：簡單易用、過程穩妥的 LINE 備份軟件</h2><p class="p1">好多雲端備份、還原容易出現千奇百怪，又難於理解的不明錯誤，穩定性、速度都存在疑問。而用 iCareFone Transfer 軟件為你備份 LINE 到電腦，不佔用任何雲端空間，而且快捷穩定，可為你的 LINE 備份資料，還原到 iPhone, iPad，更可從 Android 裝置轉移到 iOS，可說是不錯的 LINE 備份方案。</p><p class="p1">iCareFone Transfer 軟件下載／詳情：<a href="https://www.tenorshare.tw/products/line-transfer.html">按此</a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
